comments: Haliburton (SAC) makes incidental contact with Lowry (MIA) that does not dislodge him from his position.
Yurtseven (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fox (SAC) and incidental contact occurs prior to the defensive switch.
Martin (MIA) reaches in and makes marginal contact to Fox's (SAC) arm that does not affect his ability to make the pass to his teammate Barnes (SAC).
Fox (SAC) is late to the spot and not established in a legal guarding position when contact occurs with Lowry (MIA).
Yurtseven (MIA) legally contests Hield's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Jones (SAC) brings his arms forward and makes marginal contact with Butler's (MIA) non-shooting arm that does not affect his shot attempt.
Herro (MIA) makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Yurtseven (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Barnes (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Butler (MIA) extends his arm into Jones (SAC) after the release of his shot attempt, but the contact is marginal and does not affect Jones' ability to contest the shot.
